Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:40.23,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I ono čoskoro zmizne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:48.41,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,This is a bit sudden, but we've got a question from Nomura-san in Musashino, Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:50.19,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.37,0:23:55.97,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,My grandma is at her wit's end now that they've started defaulting on her pension payments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:24:03.32,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,From what I've heard, Rika-san is over a\Nhundred years old, but is she getting a pension?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:07.13,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,Are you crazy? You're getting it fundamentally wrong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:11.17,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,I'm not a hundred years old, I've just {\i1}lived{\i0\fscx140} {\r}for over a hundred years, that's all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:14.74,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,I mean, do I look like a hundred-year-old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.74,0:24:15.90,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,I'm a child, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.90,0:24:18.74,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,Kids don't pay into pensions and they don't receive them either!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:20.39,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,And that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:24.47,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,Next episode: Massacre Chapter,\NPart 6: Strong Will
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:30.37,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,But, doesn't living for a hundred years mean you're a hundred years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.37,0:24:32.76,D.Rika,D.Rika,0,0,0,,Want to try this injection just once?{Jigoku Shoujo reference - 一本、打って見る}
